{"type": "article", "id": 15021, "title": "Lavu 灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-17T08:45:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000326npoiVZ6WxQd7Duk9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯的外形像一个帐篷，它的名字“ Lavu ”指的就是古代斯堪的纳维亚人用木材和驯鹿皮临时搭建的住所。上面露出的灯泡很有艺术感，是模拟了帐篷上飘散的烟。灯罩采用 Tyvek 材料，里面也有一个灯源，透过灯罩发出温暖的光，就好像有人住在里面，很有家的气息。这盏灯可以拆分成 6 个部件和两个灯泡，方便安装。<a href=\"http://www.lavulamp.com/#top\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142358guFVO6j7Da8Cqn5h.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142358ESBcigDzqPardUNu.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142359wCKE7QbsTupG6Adg.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142359M9VesTY5Ckz1r7Dc.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142400tafMwF8pbDW7i1K5.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}